import React from 'react';
import './ComponenteInicio.css';
import {Card, Container, Navbar, FormControl, Button, Form, } from 'react-bootstrap';

const ComponenteInicio = () => {
    return (
      <Container className='wrapComponente'>
      <Card className="text-white color-bg">
         <Card.Img className='imgInicio' src='https://assets.ey.com/content/dam/ey-sites/ey-com/en_us/topics/real-estate-hospitality-and-construction/ey-high-angle-of-buildings.jpg' alt="edificios" />
         <Card.ImgOverlay>
           <Container>
           <Navbar className='position-absolute color-nav1 displayB'>
            <Card.Title class="wrapTitulo">Encontr√° tu Lugar</Card.Title>
              <Container>
                <Form.Select aria-label="Default select example">
                        <option>Departamento</option>
                        <option>Casa</option>
                        <option>Oficina Comercial</option>
                        <option>Local Comercial</option>
                </Form.Select>
                <Form className="d-flex">
                  <FormControl
                    type="search"
                    placeholder="Ubicacionn"
                    className="me-2"
                    aria-label="Ubicacion"
                  />
                  <Button variant="primary">Buscar</Button></Form>
              </Container>
           </Navbar>
           </Container>
         </Card.ImgOverlay>
      </Card>
      </Container>
  );
}

export default ComponenteInicio;

//export 'default' (imported as 'Header') was not found in './Componentes/Header.jsx' (module has no exports)
